Download
========

The source code of the latest version of DiVinE is available for download.
Binaries are only available for 32-bit Windows.  Please note that DiVinE
Cluster and DiVinE Multi-Core have been discontinued and that ProbDiVinE is
distributed as a part of the main DiVinE package.

Download: **[divine-2.5.2.tar.gz] [1]**.  An installer for 32 bit windows:
**[divine-2.5-win32.exe] [3]**.

The current *development* version is **[divine-2.92.tar.gz] [4]** (3.0 alpha
2). Binaries of development snapshots can be [obtained from hydra] [5].

Please consult [release notes] [2] for a summary of changes between releases.

[1]: download/divine-2.5.2.tar.gz
[2]: whatsnew.html
[3]: download/divine-2.5-win32.exe
[4]: download/divine-2.92.tar.gz
[5]: http://divine.fi.muni.cz/hydra/jobset/divine/mainline-debug

Alternatively, you can obtain the latest source code for DiVinE 2.x by fetching
it directly from our version control system. If you have the [darcs] [1] system
installed then the latest source code tarball can be obtained as follows:

    darcs get http://divine.fi.muni.cz/darcs/mainline divine

